dc_description_s: Shows international and administrative boundaries, four classes of roads and three classes of railroads. Relief shown by contours, gradient tints and spot heights. "Stand: 1930 - 41, Einzelne Nachträge 1942 Nur für den Dienstgebrauch!" "IV. 1942 (D 37)." Map surveyed 1930-41. Prepared for the use of the German Army. The roads are oveprinted. Princeton University Map Collection is missing sheet 1, and 5.
